Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.31,0:00:02.81,Narration,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}My name's Shin'ichi Kudo.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.81,0:00:06.55,Narration,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}I'm a famous high school detective\Nwho's solved countless cases!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.55,0:00:08.99,Narration,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}I solved a roller coaster murder case\Nwith no difficulty at all,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.99,0:00:11.99,Narration,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}but then a mysterious organization\Nforced me to take a strange poison.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.99,0:00:12.99,Narration,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}Things looked really bad!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.99,0:00:15.12,Narration,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}Ran! What's going to happen to me?!
