Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.10,0:01:55.31,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Are you alright, little boy?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.31,0:01:56.98,Thoughts,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}Little boy?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.98,0:01:58.71,Thoughts,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}What're these guys talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.71,0:02:00.75,Thoughts,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}I'm a 2nd year high school student!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.75,0:02:03.25,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,How did you get that cut on your head?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.25,0:02:04.95,Thoughts,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}Cut?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.95,0:02:06.32,Thoughts,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}Oh yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.32,0:02:08.18,Thoughts,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}A man dressed in black hit me and—
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.06,0:02:11.39,Thoughts,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}What the...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.39,0:02:13.53,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,We've found an injured boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.53,0:02:15.29,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, he's a grade school student.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.29,0:02:17.90,Thoughts,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}Who's a grade school student?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.90,0:02:19.36,Thoughts,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}What're they talking about?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.36,0:02:21.03,Thoughts,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}These officers are acting strange!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.20,0:02:25.57,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,There may have been an incident;\Nhe's received injuries to his head.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.40,0:02:27.45,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Where did he go?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.45,0:02:28.24,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.24,0:02:29.91,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,We may have a crime on our hands! Try to find him!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.91,0:02:31.14,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.94,0:02:34.90,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}"Mouri Detective Agency"
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.31,0:02:34.90,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I'm home!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.28,0:02:37.08,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, you're back, Ran!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.08,0:02:40.35,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, Dad, can't you stop throwing trash all over?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.35,0:02:44.89,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,This is why you don't get any jobs!\NAnd why Mom ran out on you!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.89,0:02:47.22,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I choose what jobs I take.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.36,0:02:50.76,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, where's that so-called detective of yours?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.76,0:02:52.83,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Wasn't he with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.83,0:02:55.93,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,He was before we left the amusement park.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.93,0:02:57.37,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,But then...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.37,0:03:00.07,Flashback,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}Sorry, Ran! You go on ahead!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.37,0:03:04.00,Thoughts,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}What could Shin'ichi be doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.86,0:03:26.16,Thoughts,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}I haven't run that far, so why am I so out of breath?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.00,0:03:33.60,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I-I've shrunk!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.07,0:03:36.54,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,How?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.54,0:03:38.94,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, it couldn't be—
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.31,0:03:42.21,Flashback,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}We'll use this. Our organization's latest poison.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.88,0:03:46.04,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Could it be because I swallowed that pill?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.59,0:03:53.49,Radio,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}Hello, this is Shin'ichi Kudo.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.49,0:03:55.49,Radio,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}I'm away at the moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.49,0:03:57.56,Radio,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}If you're interested in hiring me, please leave your name and number...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.56,0:04:00.30,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,That's strange. He's still not home.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.30,0:04:05.07,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,He's probably out havin' dinner with his novelist dad or somethin'...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.07,0:04:08.37,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Shin'ichi's parents moved to America three years ago,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.37,0:04:10.54,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,so he's living all by himself now!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.54,0:04:12.38,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Oh yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.38,0:04:16.18,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Something must've happened to him afterward!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.18,0:04:18.18,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to stop by his house!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.18,0:04:20.15,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,W-What about my dinner?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.06,0:04:29.15,Thoughts,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}Darn it! Can't I even get into my own house?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.27,0:04:38.87,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Dr. Agasa!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.87,0:04:40.17,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.17,0:04:42.84,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,It's me! Shin'ichi!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.84,0:04:44.74,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,A relative of Shin'ichi, are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.74,0:04:46.71,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,His house is the next one over.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.71,0:04:48.55,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Shin'ichi!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.55,0:04:50.48,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Here, I'll prove it!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.48,0:04:52.05,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Your name is Hiroshi Agasa and you're 52!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.05,0:04:54.92,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You're an eccentric inventor\Nand claim that you're a genius,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.92,0:04:56.72,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,but everything you make is junk!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.72,0:04:59.49,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You also have a mole on your butt\Nthat has a hair sticking out of it!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.49,0:05:02.46,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Only Shin'ichi knows about that!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.06,0:05:05.93,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,He's been spreading my secrets around, has he?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.93,0:05:08.43,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,No! It's because I'm Shin'ichi!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.43,0:05:11.13,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I was forced to take some weird pill\Nwhich made my body shrink!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.40,0:05:12.97,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,A pill that shrunk you?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.97,0:05:13.70,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.61,0:05:18.98,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,If such a pill exists, I want to see it for myself!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.98,0:05:21.85,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You suspicious little punk!\NI'm taking you to the police!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.85,0:05:22.58,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Doc!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.58,0:05:26.12,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You tripped while hurrying on your way back\Nfrom the Colombo restaurant, didn't you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.12,0:05:28.05,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,How do you know that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.05,0:05:29.52,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Your clothes, Doc.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.52,0:05:32.96,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,The front of your clothes is still wet,\Nyet the back is completely dry!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.96,0:05:35.29,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,That's evidence that you were running in the rain.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.29,0:05:37.60,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,What's more, you also have mud on your pants.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.60,0:05:39.56,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,The only street in this area where you could get mud on you
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.56,0:05:42.13,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,is in front of Colombo,\Nwhich is under construction!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.13,0:05:45.69,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Plus some of Colombo's special meat sauce is still in your mustache.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.14,0:05:48.77,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,W-Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.48,0:05:52.74,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Elementary, my dear Agasa!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.74,0:05:55.77,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,S-Shin'ichi?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.38,0:05:58.82,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.82,0:06:05.29,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,So the uncompleted poison mysteriously caused your body to shrink.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.29,0:06:07.09,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,That's the gist of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.09,0:06:10.55,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Talk about lame. My clothes from when I was a kid fit perfectly.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.03,0:06:13.43,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I'm begging you, Doc! You are a genius, after all!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.43,0:06:16.63,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Make me some medicine that'll change me back to normal!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.63,0:06:20.24,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Hold on there! I don't even know the ingredients of the pill you took...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.24,0:06:22.41,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Then all we need to do is figure out where those guys are
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.41,0:06:24.28,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,and get some of those pills!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.28,0:06:26.77,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Well, that would certainly help...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.18,0:06:28.51,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Listen, Shin'ichi!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.51,0:06:30.42,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,If they find out you're still alive,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.42,0:06:33.05,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,they'll come back to put an end to you for good!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.05,0:06:35.75,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,So this must stay a secret\Nbetween just the two of us!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.75,0:06:37.32,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You mustn't tell anyone at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.32,0:06:39.16,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,That means not even Ran-{\i1}kun{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.16,0:06:41.06,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Shin'ichi! Are you there?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.06,0:06:42.23,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,It's Ran!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.23,0:06:43.93,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Oh no! Hide quickly!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.93,0:06:46.29,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,If you're home, then you can at least answer the phone!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.70,0:06:50.94,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Dr. Agasa? Where's Shin'ichi?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.94,0:06:52.94,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Uh, well, he's...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.94,0:06:52.94,Thoughts,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}Dad's glasses...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.94,0:06:54.28,Thoughts,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}Disguise time!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.94,0:06:54.28,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}He isn't here?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.28,0:06:55.70,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa, these are strong!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.05,0:06:58.13,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Is there someone there?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.81,0:07:01.88,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You must be really shy!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.88,0:07:04.14,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Come on now, face this way!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.48,0:07:07.61,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,He's...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.49,0:07:11.15,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,...so cute!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.19,0:07:14.29,Thoughts,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}Her chest!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.29,0:07:15.39,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Who is this boy?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.39,0:07:18.16,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,He belongs to a distant relative of mine!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.16,0:07:19.23,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,What's your name?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.23,0:07:22.60,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,M-My name's Shin—
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.60,0:07:24.23,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Err...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.81,0:07:28.71,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Conan!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.71,0:07:31.38,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,My name's Conan Edogawa!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.38,0:07:33.97,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Conan? That's an odd name.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.28,0:07:38.11,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,My dad was a big fan of Conan Doyle, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.35,0:07:40.92,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Reminds me of Shin'ichi somehow...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.92,0:07:42.35,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Ran-{\i1}kun{\i0}, I almost forgot!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.35,0:07:45.86,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Do you think you could let him stay\Nat your house for a little while?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.86,0:07:47.86,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,What the heck are you—
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.86,0:07:50.16,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,His parents are in the hospital\Nafter getting into an accident...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.16,0:07:54.87,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,They asked me to look after him,\Nbut I live a bachelor's life, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.87,0:07:57.60,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Sure, but I'll have to ask my dad first.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.60,0:08:00.14,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Right! So you're willing to take him in?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.14,0:08:01.74,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't that great news, Conan?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.74,0:08:05.48,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,What happens if Ran finds out\Nwho I really am while I'm there?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.48,0:08:07.58,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,The first step to turning you back to normal
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.58,0:08:11.54,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,is finding the men in black\Nwho used that drug on you!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.82,0:08:14.08,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,And Ran-{\i1}kun{\i0}'s house is a detective agency!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.22,0:08:16.59,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Her dad might run across\Ninformation about them!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.59,0:08:17.88,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Exactly!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.26,0:08:25.03,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Say, Conan-{\i1}kun{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.03,0:08:27.17,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.17,0:08:29.37,Thoughts,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}I'll never get used to this name!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.37,0:08:31.27,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Is there anyone you like?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.27,0:08:34.71,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Like a girl at school or someone?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.71,0:08:37.20,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,No, none at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.41,0:08:40.57,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,There's someone I really like, though!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.48,0:08:45.94,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Don't tell me it's that Shin'ichi boy\Nyou were looking for earlier?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.59,0:08:48.85,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,That's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.59,0:08:52.32,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,He's always been kind of a tease since he was a kid,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.32,0:08:53.86,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,and he's always been so full of himself\Nand a big mystery geek,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.86,0:09:00.50,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,but he's also courageous, cool, and dependable!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.50,0:09:04.03,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I really like Shin'ichi a lot!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.00,0:09:08.73,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,But keep this a secret from him!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.01,0:09:12.84,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Here we are! This is my house!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.84,0:09:15.48,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,It's almost like I've gained a cute little brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.48,0:09:18.28,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,It's like I can talk to you\Nabout anything, Conan-{\i1}kun{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.28,0:09:20.02,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Ran...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.02,0:09:22.88,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Let me introduce you to my dad! Follow me!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.12,0:09:26.56,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Um, Ran...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.43,0:09:29.95,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I-I'm actually...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.23,0:09:33.06,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I'm really...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.06,0:09:34.97,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I got one! I got one!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.97,0:09:36.80,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Dad!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.54,0:09:39.37,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,My first job in 6 months!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.37,0:09:41.27,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Someone kidnapped a rich guy's daughter!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.27,0:09:42.84,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Some guy dressed in black!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.84,0:09:45.71,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,A man dressed in black?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.75,0:09:50.65,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Taxi!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.65,0:09:53.14,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Conan-{\i1}kun{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.12,0:09:59.86,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,This case is calling my name!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.86,0:10:03.69,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Calling for the famous detective known as Kogoro Mouri!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.53,0:10:07.43,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you here?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.43,0:10:09.47,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Because he got in before I could stop him!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.47,0:10:11.87,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I'm riding in a car! Yay!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.87,0:10:13.07,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,So who is he?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.07,0:10:15.07,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,He belongs to a relative of Dr. Agasa!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.07,0:10:17.28,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I don't need you bothering me while I work! Get out!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.28,0:10:20.27,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,We can't get out! We're on a freeway!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.15,0:10:25.68,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,The person kidnapped was my only daughter.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.68,0:10:28.02,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Akiko Tani. 10 years old.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.02,0:10:31.12,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,My butler Asao saw the perpetrator with his own eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.12,0:10:33.42,Thoughts,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}Darn, I can't see the picture.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.42,0:10:35.32,Thoughts,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}Being so small is such a pain!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.83,0:10:40.70,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,What was the surrounding situation like when she was kidnapped?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.70,0:10:42.47,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Who is this boy?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.47,0:10:44.50,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Just an acquaintance...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.50,0:10:46.97,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Ran! Watch him!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.97,0:10:50.27,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Well then, Asao-{\i1}san{\i0}, please explain in detail what happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.27,0:10:55.18,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,It occurred when she went to play outside after returning from school.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.35,0:11:00.25,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,A man dressed in black suddenly appeared from a corner of the garden!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.99,0:11:03.09,Flashback,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}Give this message to her father.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.09,0:11:08.13,Flashback,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}If he wants his daughter back, he'll shut down his company for 1 month.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.13,0:11:11.69,Flashback,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}Get the police involved and she's as good as dead!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.00,0:11:13.26,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Upon leaving those words,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.26,0:11:15.77,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,the kidnapper scaled a pine tree and escaped outside!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.77,0:11:18.10,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Did this man have any special characteristics?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.10,0:11:20.44,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,My eyes aren't what they used to be, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.44,0:11:22.10,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,That's too bad...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.04,0:11:27.94,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You shouldn't get in the way of my dad's work, Conan-{\i1}kun{\i0}...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.15,0:11:32.75,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Did anyone else hear the kidnapper's voice or any sounds out of the ordinary?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.75,0:11:39.31,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,No. Other than Asao-{\i1}san{\i0}'s shouts for help, it was completely quiet.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.46,0:11:42.79,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Which means Asao-{\i1}san{\i0} was the only one who saw the perpetrator.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.79,0:11:47.13,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Judging from the demands, the kidnapper is likely someone from a rival company.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.13,0:11:51.07,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it! To think they would want money on top of that demand!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.07,0:11:51.96,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Money?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.96,0:11:54.17,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,There was a phone call just now!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.17,0:11:56.84,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,They demanded that I prepare 300 million, all in used bills!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.84,0:11:59.24,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,There must be some sort of mistake, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.24,0:12:01.21,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Silence! You will remain quiet!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.21,0:12:05.32,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Which companies stand to gain something if your company shuts down?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.32,0:12:08.95,Thoughts,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}There's something not right about this incident.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.95,0:12:11.89,Thoughts,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}Why did the perpetrator kidnap her inside her home?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.09,0:12:14.89,Thoughts,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}It would've been easier on her way home from school.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.89,0:12:18.66,Thoughts,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}And being clearly seen is too careless.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.30,0:12:24.26,Thoughts,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}But demanding used bills is oddly cautious...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.87,0:12:27.87,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, you're really good at soccer, Conan-{\i1}kun{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.87,0:12:29.37,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I guess so.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.37,0:12:33.08,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Shin'ichi would do that whenever he was thinking about something.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.08,0:12:35.98,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,He said it would get his mind working.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.98,0:12:38.61,Thoughts,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}That Shin'ichi is me!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.89,0:12:47.08,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Conan-{\i1}kun{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.46,0:12:57.26,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,How rare it is for Jumbo to be friendly with a stranger.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.70,0:13:04.80,Thoughts,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}The kidnapper climbed this pine tree to break in and to get out.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.18,0:13:08.85,Thoughts,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}Which means this dog {\i1}must{\i0} have barked at him!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.85,0:13:11.41,Thoughts,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}That's it! I've figured this case out!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.98,0:13:15.79,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,It sounds like this dog barks at all strangers, doesn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.79,0:13:19.72,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. Jumbo is one of the best guard dogs around, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.72,0:13:21.86,Thoughts,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}Wait, the servants said that it was completely quiet
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.86,0:13:25.12,Thoughts,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}except for when the butler was yelling!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.57,0:13:30.69,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,And where are you going, Asao-{\i1}san{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.10,0:13:34.11,Thoughts,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}He realized it!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.11,0:13:37.27,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,There's something strange about your story!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.27,0:13:42.41,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,The kidnapper snuck in, took the girl,\Nand escaped using that tree!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.41,0:13:44.78,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Yet the guard dog didn't bark!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.78,0:13:46.38,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,T-That's because...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.38,0:13:50.59,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Plus your testimony is too full of ambiguity!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.59,0:13:55.18,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Was there really a man dressed in black, Asao-{\i1}san{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.19,0:13:58.92,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Or shall I say, Kidnapper!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.03,0:14:01.70,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Asao! How dare you!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.70,0:14:03.93,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,My deepest apologies, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.93,0:14:05.80,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,What did you do this for?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.80,0:14:07.47,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Did someone put you up to it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.47,0:14:10.74,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,No, I did this entirely of my own accord!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.74,0:14:13.61,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,So where is the girl now?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.61,0:14:15.20,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,A nearby hotel...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.52,0:14:19.72,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Case closed!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.72,0:14:25.16,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,With Detective Kogoro Mouri on the job, no case goes unsolved!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.42,0:14:28.73,Thoughts,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}No! It's not over yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.73,0:14:31.99,Thoughts,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}There's still another side to this case!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.61,0:14:46.11,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Sir! There's a phone call!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.11,0:14:48.71,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I'm busy. Tell them to call back later!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.71,0:14:50.27,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,B-But...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.68,0:14:52.55,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,This is Tani.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.55,0:14:54.68,Radio,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}Is the 300 million ready?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.72,0:14:58.24,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Who is this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.19,0:15:01.46,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I called earlier.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.46,0:15:03.89,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I'm the guy who kidnapped your daughter.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.89,0:15:06.53,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,That's impossible! The kidnapper has already—
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.53,0:15:08.36,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,So you did have help!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.36,0:15:11.30,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,No, I did it alone! Please believe me!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.07,0:15:14.87,Thoughts,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}This man is telling the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.87,0:15:18.54,Thoughts,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}After being kidnapped for the first time,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.54,0:15:22.60,Thoughts,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}she was most likely kidnapped again by someone else.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.11,0:15:25.11,Thoughts,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}By someone much worse!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.11,0:15:26.58,Radio,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}Daddy! Help!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.58,0:15:27.91,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Akiko!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.85,0:15:31.89,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I'm an impatient man.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.89,0:15:34.22,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry and get the 300 million ready
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.22,0:15:36.66,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,or there's no telling what'll happen to your daughter.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.66,0:15:39.10,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Please! I'll get the money somehow!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.10,0:15:41.76,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Just give Akiko back unharmed!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.93,0:15:45.39,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Keep him talking and try to find out his location!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.64,0:15:46.54,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,His location?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.54,0:15:48.40,Radio,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}Who's that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.40,0:15:49.91,Radio,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}Don't tell me it's the police.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.91,0:15:51.77,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,No! It isn't...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.77,0:15:53.91,Radio,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}Daddy! I'm in a storeroom of a school!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.91,0:15:56.18,Radio,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}I can see a big chimney from the window—
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.18,0:15:57.28,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Akiko!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.28,0:15:59.18,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I'll call again in one hour.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.18,0:16:01.05,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Get the money ready by then!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.75,0:16:04.22,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Big-mouthed brat.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.09,0:16:08.66,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,A big chimney visible from a school storeroom
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.66,0:16:11.36,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,isn't enough information to pinpoint which school it is...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.36,0:16:15.20,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,At any rate, please buy us some time by preparing the money.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.20,0:16:16.60,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,R-Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.30,0:16:22.81,Thoughts,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}The kidnapper's nervous now that we know his location!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.81,0:16:25.17,Thoughts,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}If we don't rescue the little girl soon...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.17,0:16:27.58,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,What're you doing, Conan-{\i1}kun{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.58,0:16:30.38,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,It hasn't been very long since she was kidnapped,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.38,0:16:33.28,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,so I figured they might be somewhere nearby...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.28,0:16:34.42,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,That's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.42,0:16:38.02,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,There's no way he could have gotten far with a little girl with him!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.02,0:16:41.42,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,If we limit it to the nearby area, that leaves only so many schools to check!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.56,0:16:43.39,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Conan-{\i1}kun{\i0}, where are you going?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.39,0:16:44.81,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Ran! After that dog!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.81,0:16:45.86,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.97,0:16:52.50,Thoughts,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}The chimney she sees is probably either a factory or a bathhouse!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.50,0:16:55.90,Thoughts,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}There are only 5 schools in the area where you can see chimneys!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.32,0:17:10.45,Thoughts,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}No!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.45,0:17:12.32,Thoughts,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}No!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.32,0:17:14.06,Thoughts,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}Not here either!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.06,0:17:17.08,Thoughts,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}Darn it! It wasn't any of them!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.53,0:17:20.16,Thoughts,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}There aren't any other schools that have views of chimneys!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.16,0:17:22.32,Thoughts,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}They must not be in this area after all!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.94,0:17:29.27,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Wait a second! Just maybe...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.12,0:17:50.09,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,This is it!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.09,0:17:53.29,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,She saw this building from the side\Nand mistook it for a chimney!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.53,0:17:57.47,Thoughts,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}Schools in this vicinity that have a side view of this building...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.10,0:18:00.80,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Futatsubashi Middle School!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.17,0:18:05.17,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Place the money on the bench in Hyakujii Park.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.17,0:18:07.34,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Once I have it in my hands, I'll return the girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.34,0:18:09.35,Radio,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}Let me hear Akiko's voice one more time!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.08,0:18:12.24,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You'll have plenty of time later to hear it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.72,0:18:15.55,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,We've come to an agreement.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.55,0:18:18.71,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Which means your role is just about over with.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.09,0:18:24.18,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Not so fast!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.13,0:18:28.73,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Who's there?! Where are you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.73,0:18:29.89,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Right here!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.84,0:18:39.07,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,It's alright now.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.07,0:18:40.68,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.68,0:18:41.81,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Shin'ichi Kudo—
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.81,0:18:45.87,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I mean, Conan Edogawa. A detective!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.22,0:18:47.84,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,A detective?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.75,0:18:54.95,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be mockin' me, you little brat!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.86,0:19:02.92,Thoughts,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}Darn it! I can't put any power into it with my body so small!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.80,0:19:07.17,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,How about this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.17,0:19:10.66,Thoughts,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}No good! My soccer kicks have weakened too!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.78,0:19:22.15,Thoughts,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}Even if I do find the criminals,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.15,0:19:26.39,Thoughts,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}in my smaller body I can't even capture them or beat them up!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.39,0:19:29.23,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Playtime's over! Say your prayers!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.23,0:19:31.32,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.80,0:19:34.42,Thoughts,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}It's all over!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.43,0:19:37.59,Thoughts,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}Ran!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.08,0:19:52.18,Thoughts,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}Talk about strong!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.18,0:19:53.82,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Everything's okay now!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.82,0:19:55.48,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,How did you know to come here?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.48,0:19:59.01,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I followed you and then I saw Jumbo jump out from here!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.96,0:20:03.63,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Jumbo!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.63,0:20:06.96,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,So you're the one behind this!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.96,0:20:11.66,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Kidnapping case?\NDetective Kogoro Mouri is your man!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.97,0:20:13.76,Thoughts,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}Gimme a break.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.44,0:20:21.40,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I was the one who came up with the idea to kidnap me!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.64,0:20:23.81,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.81,0:20:27.98,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Daddy's always too busy with work to care about me...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.98,0:20:32.19,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,So I had Asao-{\i1}san{\i0} "kidnap" me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.19,0:20:34.22,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I thought I could get Daddy\Nto spend time with me
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.22,0:20:36.89,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,if his company had to take a break!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.96,0:20:43.49,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I see. So the first kidnapping was a fake.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.83,0:20:45.90,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Even if my daughter did ask for your help,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.90,0:20:48.37,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I find it difficult to forgive what you've done!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.37,0:20:49.74,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I assume you realize this, Asao?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.74,0:20:51.34,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.34,0:20:52.17,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,As punishment,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.17,0:20:54.74,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,you will make arrangements for a\None-week trip that starts tomorrow!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.74,0:20:57.75,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,A trip to Australia, where Akiko has always wanted to go!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.75,0:20:59.65,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,S-Sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.65,0:21:03.15,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,She and I will be going there together, of course!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.15,0:21:04.48,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Daddy!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.76,0:21:10.66,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Letting the dog go so he could find my daughter was a stroke of genius.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.66,0:21:12.83,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You truly are a great detective!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.83,0:21:16.67,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,No, it's because of all the experience I've had!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.67,0:21:20.27,Thoughts,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}Who are you to talk?\N{\i1}I{\i0} was the one who found him...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.27,0:21:22.87,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I will express my gratitude to you another day.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.87,0:21:24.86,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Right! I'm looking forward to it!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.24,0:21:29.57,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks, Mr. Detective!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.05,0:21:33.28,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Detective?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.28,0:21:38.08,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,No, she means him, not me!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.86,0:21:45.45,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Say, Dad, about this boy...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.89,0:21:48.95,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Dr. Agasa asked if we would take care of him...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.10,0:21:54.30,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You're against it?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.87,0:21:57.01,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Sure thing!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.01,0:22:00.81,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I got a job the instant he showed up,\Nand then I solved it like an ace!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.81,0:22:02.71,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,He just might be a god of good fortune!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.71,0:22:06.37,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Stay with us and become my son!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.89,0:23:52.49,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I just transferred here!\NMy name's Conan Edogawa!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.49,0:23:54.01,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Nice to meet you!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.42,0:23:59.33,Thoughts,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}I have to go back to grade school again?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.25,0:24:04.02,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,The one responsible...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.02,0:24:06.32,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,...is you!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.32,0:24:10.15,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,If Shin'ichi were here, he'd easily solve this case.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.89,0:24:15.83,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Where could that mystery nerd have gone?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.83,0:24:16.76,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Hot!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.76,0:24:19.20,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Mouri-{\i1}kun{\i0}! You were right!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.20,0:24:21.73,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I've changed my mind about you,\N"Great Detective"!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.73,0:24:25.71,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I could never do that. I could never\Nbe as strong as Yoko-{\i1}san{\i0}...
