Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.71,0:24:31.72,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(320,200)\bord0\shad0\b0\fsp0\fnDINk\fs32\c&HEFDFCF&}The Celebrity Locked Room Murder Case
Dialogue: 0,0:24:31.72,0:24:36.68,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(500,204)\c&H000000&\bord0\shad0\b0\fnLos Altos II\fs24}Ice
Dialogue: 0,0:24:31.72,0:24:36.68,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Next Conan's Hint: Ice
Dialogue: 0,0:24:36.68,0:24:41.69,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(320,440)\fnSegoe\fscx100\bord0\shad0\fs24}Look forward to the next episode
Dialogue: 0,0:24:37.74,0:24:39.45,Dialogue,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Will you win against me next time?
